        "subject": "LU-3564 lod: add update records to recovery list",
        "message": "LU-3564 lod: add update records to recovery list\n\nAdd update records to the obd recovery list, which\nis attached to lu_target, so recovery thread\n(target_recover_thread()) can choose req or update\nby transno during recovery.\n\nAdd update_recovery.c to handle updates replay during\nrecovery.\n\nChange-Id: I74e8bab06a733cd17a42fef875e62b7e59442766\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\n"
